    "### Creating the Crew\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Memory\n",
    "- Setting `memory=True` when putting the crew together enables Memory."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "metadata": {
    "height": 115
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "crew = Crew(\n",
    "  agents=[support_agent, support_quality_assurance_agent],\n",
    "  tasks=[inquiry_resolution, quality_assurance_review],\n",
    "  verbose=2,\n",
    "  memory=True\n",
    ")"
